            "title": "《大手成交》中國平安一手約84萬股交叉盤,涉資3878萬元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社23日專訊》中國平安(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02318:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02318\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02318-HK</a>)於1:51pm錄得1手84.35萬股交叉盤,每股造45.975元,較上日收市價高0.2%,涉資3878萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　中國平安現價升0.2%,報46元;成交1509萬股,成交金額6.95億元,主動買沽比率55:45,資金淨主動買入6739萬元。(rw)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
